profile: Ceramic Decor is the largest tile and stone showroom in the Guelph-Kitchener-Waterloo-Cambridge area.  The family owned company has been in business since 1983 and has a steadily growing staff of 30 employees.  Ceramic Decor has a fully stocked warehouse outlet and the largest in-stock inventory outside of Toronto.  We offer life-time warranty on all installations and also offer free advice to the "Do-it-yourselfer".  Visit our website at www.ceramicdecor.com.
